PHP Transaction Client v1.6.1 API Specification

Country Codes

The following is a list of country code constants provided by the PHP Transaction Client for use with the TransactionRequest.setBillCountryCode() and TransactionRequest.setShipCountryCode() methods. To use these constants, you must import the CountryCodes.php file.
